{"tid":2436160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"微軟電郵系統被入侵 消息指至少3萬美國組織受影響","createTime":"2021-03-07T01:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T02:41:43.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"48130dee9c717c592125ae127b4dc81dfef84bf4","tid":2436160,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:36:24.000Z","msg":"微軟電郵系統被入侵 消息指至少3萬美國組織受影響<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/2015451/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F2015451%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=2226e807\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F2015451%2F&h=9bc3a5d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/2015451/</a><br />\n<br />\n微軟公司日前證實黑客藉其電郵軟件入侵美國機構竊密。如今風暴擴大，白宮表示，受害者已多到令人擔憂的數量。熟知美國政府因應的消息人士說，至少3萬美國組織受到影響，影響遍及全球。據報黑客攻擊的受害者包括大量的小型企業、城市和地方政府。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">自今年1月以來，據稱來自中國的黑客組織一直利用4個先前未知的漏洞入侵微軟的Microsoft Exchange Server電郵伺服器，不必寄發任何惡意電郵或在電郵中附加惡意程式，就可從遠端無聲無息地竊取使用者收件夾的資訊。微軟稱這個黑客團體為Hafnium，擁有高技術，非常熟練。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n截至目前為止，僅有極少數受害組織曝光。微軟日前表示，黑客的目標包括美國的高等教育機構、國防承包商、法律事務所、傳染病研究員、政策智庫及非政府組織等。<br />\n<br />\n戴爾科技的網絡安全公司SecureWorks研究人員表示，2月28日當天，入侵情況在一夜間激增。對此，其他人的解讀是，黑客之所以加緊腳步行動，是因為他們知道自己快要曝光了。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">據悉大部分黑客行動集中在美國，但受害者遍及全球。亞洲和歐洲有數以萬計組織也受到黑客攻擊影響。<br />\n<br />\n挪威當局表示，已在境內發現黑客工具，但使用狀況不多。掌管網絡事務的歐洲官員在簡報中說，捷克布拉格市政當局和捷克勞工暨社會福利部也受影響。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n美國白宮發言人普薩基回應中國政府被指支持黑客，利用微軟電郵系統漏洞，偷取美國組織資料，指這重大漏洞或造成深遠影響，並形容今次是黑客主動作出威脅。普薩基已要求使用這系統的政府部門、私營和學術機構，馬上更新系統以作修補。<br />\n<br />\n普薩基又指，美國「網絡安全和基礎設施安全局」早前已發布緊急指令，事態仍在發展中，政府正研究下一步措施。<br />\n<br />\n普薩基告訴記者：「這是一個嚴重漏洞，可能產生深遠的影響，我們擔心有大量的受害者。」"},{"pid":"4c9091dc3000d4e6bcba0ad9d0c5a6448d361b52","tid":2436160,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6aa2e6c862f3b3959da74f95283c5022947fc2","tid":2436160,"uid":69544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:44:11.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦，美國班友自己攞嚟衰。最好，拿拿臨比支那搞爆美國。"},{"pid":"ee94ae6d404ad13a99abde6d71784c126ee9ded8","tid":2436160,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:49:35.000Z","msg":"微軟<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"3dced5b267c1860e20a9424bed99c7b02d6fcd72","tid":2436160,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:52:42.000Z","msg":"直覺話俾我知，係微軟自己放料俾中共，然後話俾人入侵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34ccad6eebdb2e63d2fc22a8d9f177aebf10bca","tid":2436160,"uid":295224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/usa-american-china-flags-merged-relationship-concept-168194750.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.dreamstime.com%2Fb%2Fusa-american-china-flags-merged-relationship-concept-168194750.jpg&h=ad18182d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你也是中國人 畜生!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab609b8164f2ec5e2a4086e5939939bcce2ea372","tid":2436160,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:58:52.000Z","msg":"自己人邊算入侵"},{"pid":"8c89c48a7486557433ca8501f511f2e613f9b04c","tid":2436160,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd6aa2e6c862f3b3959da74f95283c5022947fc2","tid":2436160,"uid":69544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:44:11.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦，美國班友自己攞嚟衰。最好，拿拿臨比支那搞爆美國。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"發悔氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國都收皮 你走佬去邊撚度都冇用"},{"pid":"601f74b1bd8edcd846c477cdd249a461db381bf3","tid":2436160,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62520d56449d901da0733c2469124f3be42950d","tid":2436160,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:41:43.000Z","msg":"是旦啦,我個hotmail都係得啲垃圾電郵."}]}